This paper focuses on measuring and analyzing the characteristics of YouTube videos, which involves aspects such as access patterns, ratings, comments, and social networking. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Networked Information Systems (cs.NI), Software Development (cs.SD), and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories.
